<span id="freeTextContainer18023211853263886224"><strong>Humbling and Inspiring </strong><br/><br/>At the very least, Bob Goff is an incredibly engaging storyteller teller. Often I laughed out loud wild shaking g my head in amazement at the things he did. But more than anything he is filled with a no holds barred love to do right in the world, to spread the love in both large and small actions as easily and willingly as the rest of us breathe. I’m a better person for having met Bob through this book. My new daily mantra is “Love does” a call to action. Less sitting abou</span>
  <span id="freeText18023211853263886224" style="display:none"><strong>Humbling and Inspiring </strong><br /><br />At the very least, Bob Goff is an incredibly engaging storyteller teller. Often I laughed out loud wild shaking g my head in amazement at the things he did. But more than anything he is filled with a no holds barred love to do right in the world, to spread the love in both large and small actions as easily and willingly as the rest of us breathe. I’m a better person for having met Bob through this book. My new daily mantra is “Love does” a call to action. Less sitting about thinking (not necessarily easy in these COVID-19 times) and more action. </span>
